# prose_translation = Our subject is the art of poetry itself and its various species, with the specific character of each; the way in which plots should be constructed if the poem is to be successful; the number and nature of its component parts; and similarly all other matters within this field of inquiry. Let us follow the natural order and begin with the primary facts.
# literal_translation = Concerning poetic art itself and the forms of it, what sort of power each has, and how it is necessary for the plots to be composed if the poetry is going to hold well, further and from how many and what kind of parts it is, and similarly also concerning the other things as many as are of the same method, let us speak, having begun according to nature first from the first things.
