# prose_translation = They differ from one another in three respects: either by using different means for the imitation, or by imitating different things, or by imitating in a different manner and not in the same way.
# literal_translation = They differ but from each other in three [things], for either by in different [means] to imitate or by different [things] or by differently and not the same manner.
