# prose_translation = This has already become clear in the case of Comedy; for having constructed the plot by means of probable incidents, they then attach random names to the characters, and do not write about particular individuals as the lampooners do.
# literal_translation = Upon indeed therefore of-the comedy already this manifest has-become; having-constructed for the plot through of-the likely-things thus the happening names they-attach, and not just-as the lampoon-makers about the according-to each they-make.
