# translation_lang = en
# prose_translation = A well-constructed plot, then, must be single rather than double, as some say, and the change must be not from bad fortune to good, but on the contrary from good fortune to bad; and this should result not from depravity, but from some great error on the part of a man such as we have described, or of one better rather than worse.
