# sentence_id = 180
# document_id = 0086-034
# subdoc = 14.20
# translation_lang = en
# prose_translation = For this reason, as has long been said, tragedies are not about many families. For poets, searching not by art but by chance, found out how to provide such effects in their plots; they are therefore compelled to have recourse to those houses in which such sufferings have occurred.
# literal_translation = Through for this , which long-ago has-been-said , not concerning many families the tragedies are . Searching for not from art but from chance found the such to-provide in the myths ; they-are-compelled therefore to these the houses to-resort as-many-as the such happened sufferings .
