# prose_translation = For the story of the Odyssey is not long: a certain man being away from home for many years and watched by Poseidon and being alone, and furthermore the things at home being in such a state that his property is being consumed by suitors and his son is being plotted against, but he himself arrives after being tossed by storms, and having recognized certain people, making an attack, he himself was saved and destroyed his enemies.
