# prose_translation = Lengthened, shortened, and altered forms of words contribute in no small degree to the clarity of the diction and its removal from the commonplace; for by being different from the standard and being unusual, they produce the effect of being non-commonplace, while by their sharing in the standard form, they will be clear.
