# prose_translation = For just as the sea-battle at Salamis and the battle with the Carthaginians in Sicily took place at the same time but did not tend toward any single end, so in successive periods of time one event often follows another without their producing any single result.
# literal_translation = Just as for according to the same times the and in Salamis there-was sea-battle and the in Sicily of-Carthaginians battle nothing towards the same tending end , thus also in the successive times sometimes becomes the-one after the-other , from which one nothing becomes end .
